OL,3,CDrug driving tradesman pursued by
OL,4,Cpolice now sentenced
OL,6,FHampshire Police have released bodycam
OL,7,Ffootage of the moment Jordan Carson
OL,8,Fwas pursued by officers before finally
OL,9,Fbeing arrested.
OL,11,FA drug driving tradesman who was
OL,12,Fpursued by police at speeds of 60mph
OL,13,Fthrough Southampton, has been
OL,14,Fsentenced and banned from getting
OL,15,Fbehind the wheel for two years.
OL,17,FOfficers from the Force's proactive
OL,18,Froads policing team tried to stop
OL,19,FJordan Carson's white Transit van.
