OL,3,CDrug driving tradesman pursued by
OL,4,Cpolice now sentenced
OL,6,FAlthough the 25 year old from Spring
OL,7,FRoad, initially stopped on Upper
OL,8,FDeacon Road, he quickly changed his
OL,9,Fmind and was pursued by police through
OL,10,Fresidential streets in Sholing and
OL,11,FBitterne.
OL,13,FOne of the team followed him while
OL,14,Falso directing other units into
OL,15,Fposition, ready for Carson's attempts
OL,16,Fto run from the vehicle and avoid
OL,17,Farrest.
