OL,3,CDrug driving tradesman pursued by
OL,4,Cpolice now sentenced
OL,6,FHe stopped in Merryoak Green and tried
OL,7,Fto reverse into a police car before
OL,8,Ffleeing the vehicle, straight into the
OL,9,Fpath of an officer on foot.
OL,11,FSouthampton Crown Court heard Carson
OL,12,Fwas driving without a licence or
OL,13,Finsurance, and had also subsequently
OL,14,Ftested positive for cannabis.
OL,16,FHe was handed a one year jail term,
OL,17,Fsuspended for two years and given a
OL,18,Ftwo year ban from driving
