OL,3,CDrug driving tradesman pursued by
OL,4,Cpolice now sentenced
OL,6,FThe 25 year old was told he must take
OL,7,Fan extended retest before getting
OL,8,Fbehind the wheel again, and undertake
OL,9,F150 hours of unpaid work and 20
OL,10,Frehabilitation days.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,13,Finvestigating officer PC Jake Lawrence
OL,14,Fsaid: "Carson's arrogance led him to
OL,15,Fbelieve he was a more capable driver
OL,16,Fthan our specially trained team, and
OL,17,Fcould escape justice by leading them
OL,18,Fon a chase through a residential area.
