OL,3,CDrug driving tradesman pursued by
OL,4,Cpolice now sentenced
OL,6,FThanks to PC Scott's expertly led
OL,7,Fpursuit, he wasn't able to get away
OL,8,Fand is now paying the price for his
OL,9,Fdecision to get behind the wheel while
OL,10,Fon drugs, and without a licence or
OL,11,Finsurance.
OL,13,FThere is simply no excuse for
OL,14,Fdangerous driving on our roads, which
OL,15,Fputs the lives of other motorists in
OL,16,Fdanger."
